to build an Ark to save creation from the coming flood. Noah How to Train Your Dragon 2 Set in the mythical world of burly Vikings and wild dragons, and based on the book by Cressida Cowell, the action comedy tells the story of Hiccup, a Viking teenager who doesn\'t exactly fit in with his tribe\'s longstanding tradition of heroic dragon slayers. Hiccup\'s world is turned upside down when he encounters a dragon that challenges he and his fellow Vikings to see the world from an entirely different point of view.
Maleficent The untold story of Disney\'s most iconic villain from the 1959 classic "Sleeping Beauty." A beautiful, pure-hearted young woman with stunning black wings, Maleficent has an idyllic life growing up in a peaceable forest kingdom, until one day when an invading army of humans threatens the harmony of the land.
